org.tms.api

Interface Row

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseElement, Derivable, Listenable, TableElement, TableRowColumnElement, Taggable

    public interface Row
extends TableElement, Derivable, TableRowColumnElement
    A Table row, containing a horizontal slice of cells.

    Rows are created by calling the various flavors of addRow in the Table interface. See TableRowColumnElement and TableElement for a list of methods that all Row instances support.

    Since:
    "1.0"
    Version:
    "1.1"
